modShortDescription: This 7 Days to Die mod revive Biofuel and Human Turd. Can craft Gas Can without shale oil and call of memories to loot toilet.
modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod revive Biofuel and Human Turd. Can craft Gas Can without shale oil and call of memories to [loot](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-loot/) toilet.

**Features:**

* Can craft Biofuel from Animal Fat or Human Turd.
* Can find Human Turd at toilet.
* Can craft [Farm](https://7daystodiemods.com/farming-mods/) Plot from Human Turd.
* Can craft Gas Can from Biofuel.

[Download](https://www.mediafire.com/file/zh2qhnmwkjwvuff/BioFuel.zip)

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/16570-a18-revives-biofuel-and-turd/).

**Credits:** [Nanashi](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/nanashi/)
